contactListName.description:
Name of the contact list.

The following arguments are optional:

createdTimestamp.description: Timestamp noting when the contact list was created in ISO 8601 format.

description.description: Description of what the contact list is about.

lastUpdatedTimestamp.description: Timestamp noting the last time the contact list was updated in ISO 8601 format.

tags.description: Key-value map of resource tags for the contact list. If configured with a provider `default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

topics.description: Configuration block(s) with topic for the contact list. Detailed below.
